{"tid":1574850,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[物資] 更新一下前線情況，有心人請入","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T00:39:02.000Z","uid":137632,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1409ed3a3dd68dab312f43d12cac2ae3389208f8","tid":1574850,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"話說好耐冇人開物資post咁，小弟想就近排既局勢比啲意見<br />\n我會分低中高風險去比各位決定幫手帶啲咩去前線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">低風險</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>毛巾 (祝君安好果款可以了)<br />\n沖浪板 (Decathlon ，偏貴但做盾好用)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVCsO4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVCsO4b.jpg&h=8d87e798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>浮板(同上，但便宜啲)<br />\n冰袖 (深水埗仲有，平同有用)<br />\n面巾(深水埗仲有，平同有用)</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">中風險<br />\n</span></span><strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">玻璃樽 </span></strong></span> (重要)<br />\n噴漆 (五金鋪應該30蚊罐)<br />\n噴膠(好似40蚊罐，for文宣)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXQNO4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXQNO4A.jpg&h=ae6c9209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">高風險</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>火油、電油 (BBQ)<br />\n錘</strong><br />\n<br />\n頭盔豬咀大家私底下派其實仲會有人要，因為近排棄裝既情況都多<br />\n如果大家有咩補充幫手留言講講，一齊討論"},{"pid":"7a99f7a2ea1ebc1f7a30636f67833208b144fd7d","tid":1574850,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f085109030e67be0ea41629dec2bcbba6d7122db","tid":1574850,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"前線要物資打水炮車"},{"pid":"2a79efe81fabc812d212b6edcdc1e294914aef96","tid":1574850,"uid":263058,"like":0,"disli